>
  <section class="section content-width">
    <h1 style="font-size:var(--text-h1);">About</h1>
    <p class="reading-width" style="margin-top:var(--space-16);color:var(--color-text-secondary);">
      Junior full-stack developer working across React, TypeScript, and
      FastAPI, with an AI-assisted workflow built around engineering
      discipline: dry-run defaults, read-only modes, and honest limits. The
      full story is coming in a later implementation pass.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
